            <div class="about-content">
                <div class="about-text">
                    <p>Founded in 2018, Apex was born from a simple vision: to create headphones that deliver exceptional sound quality without compromise. Our founder, Alex Chen, an audio engineer with over 15 years of experience, was frustrated with the market's offerings â€“ headphones either sounded great but were uncomfortable, or were comfortable but compromised on sound quality.</p>
                    
